  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a ttukbaegi earthenware pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and saut\u00132 until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add ginger and garlic and saut\u00132 for 1 minute.",
    "Add dates, five spice powder, allspice, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, for 15 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in crab meat, if using.",
    "Transfer to serving bowls and garnish with sesame seeds.",
    "Serve warm, accompanied by steamed rice or roti."
